---
layout: "../layouts/Layout.astro";
title: "Join the OB1 Forum";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Join the OB1 Forum</title>
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #0f1116;
        color: #e4e4e7;
        font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      header {
        background-color: #0f1116;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: flex-end;
        gap: 2rem;
      }
      header a {
        color: #f0f6fc;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
      main {
        max-width: 640px;
        margin: 3rem auto;
        padding: 1rem;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: white;
      }
      p.intro {
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        color: #cdd0d4;
      }
      label {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: normal;
      }
      input,
      select,
      textarea {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 0.75rem;
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        background-color: #1c1f26;
        color: #f4f4f5;
      }
      button {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        background-color: #16a34a;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        cursor: pointer;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
      <a href="/forum">Forum</a>
    </header>
    <main>
      <h1>Join the OB1 Forum</h1>
      <p class="intro">
        OB1 stands for "Obekväm arbetstid" in Swedish – inconvenient working
        hours. It refers to those working unsocial shifts (nights, weekends) and
        often with limited legal protections. This space was born from lived
        experience – as a dishwasher in Malmö, winter 2024. OB1 exists to help
        people facing abuse or legal uncertainty at work find each other, share
        strategies, and solve real problems together.
      </p>
      <form method="POST" action="#">
        <label>
          Would you prefer someone from OB1 to call you directly instead of
          filling out this form?
          <select name="callInstead">
            <option value="">Yes / No</option>
            <option value="yes">Yes</option>
            <option value="no">No</option>
          </select>
        </label>
        <label
          >First name
          <input type="text" name="firstname" />
        </label>
        <label
          >Email
          <input type="email" name="email" />
        </label>
        <label
          >Phone number (optional, if you want us to call you)
          <input type="text" name="phone" />
        </label>
        <label
          >Age
          <input type="number" name="age" />
        </label>
        <label
          >Gender
          <select name="gender">
            <option>Man</option>
            <option>Woman</option>
            <option>Prefer not to say</option>
          </select>
        </label>
        <label
          >Nationality
          <input type="text" name="nationality" />
        </label>
        <label
          >Sectors you’ve worked in (check all that apply)
          <textarea
            name="sectors"
            rows="2"
            placeholder="e.g. Restaurant – Cleaner, Logistics, Delivery, Legal, Syndicalist"
          ></textarea>
        </label>
        <label
          >Where did you work and experience problems?
          <textarea name="where" rows="2" placeholder="e.g. Malmö, Quan, 2024"
          ></textarea>
        </label>
        <label
          >Do you have a work contract now? If not, what is your current status?
          <textarea name="contract"></textarea>
        </label>
        <label
          >Legal or workplace problems you’ve had (past or present)?
          <textarea name="problems"></textarea>
        </label>
        <label
          >What kind of help do you need or wish existed today?
          <textarea name="help"></textarea>
        </label>
        <label
          >How did you find this site?
          <textarea
            name="source"
            rows="2"
            placeholder="Someone told me, Blog, Social media, etc."></textarea>
        </label>
        <label
          >Would you like us to create a forum account for you in advance?
          <select name="createAccount">
            <option value="">Yes / No</option>
            <option value="yes">Yes</option>
            <option value="no">No</option>
          </select>
        </label>
        <button type="submit">Join the OB1 Forum</button>
      </form>
      <p style="margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #999">
        Disclaimer: We collect only the information needed to understand your
        situation and provide access to the forum. No data is shared externally.
        You can request full deletion anytime by contacting us.
      </p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
